% circvar computes circular variance for one vector% Allen, F. H. & Johnson, O. (1991) Automated conformational analysis from crystallographic data. 4. Statistical descriptors for a distribution of torsion angles.% Acta Cryst., B47, 62-67. % invec must be complexfunction [circvarvec] = circvar(invec)sum(real(invec)).^2Rsquare = abs(sum(invec)) ./ length(invec)circvariance = 1-Rsquare